@item
‚ùóÔ∏èWhen yanking (typically @kbd{C-y}) a regexp into an interactive prompt, you @emph{must} have the point/focus in the minibuffer prompt (typically via mouse). Otherwise the desired content can be altered with extra escaping.
@end itemize
@item
